rican Life League!</u> American Life League is the largest grassroots pro-life organization in the United States and is committed to the protection of all innocent human beings from the moment of creation to natural death. For more information or media inquiries, please contact Katie Walker at </font></strong><a href="mailto:kwalker@all.org"><strong><font size="3">kwalker@all.org</font></strong></a><strong><font size="3">.</font></strong></em></p><p><strong><font size="3"><span style="font-size: 14pt"><u><font color="#ff0000" size="4">HEADLINES</font><br /></u></span><br />
