Today, President Obama is following a game plan that has been very carefully orchestrated by his team and which, some say, will cost </font></strong><a target="_blank" href="http://webmail.rochester.rr.com/do/redirect?url=http%253A%252F%252Fnvs.all.org%252Fsendstudio%252Flink.php%253FM%253D96913%2526N%253D674%2526L%253D3347%2526F%253DH"><strong><font size="3">$150 million</font></strong></a><strong><font size="3">. But after the celebrations, the balls, the streamers and the crowds, what will his presidency mean for this nation, the pro-life movement and the world in general? <br /><br />
